<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Payment Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding: 20px;">
    <!-- Header with Larger Logo -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <img src="https://task-trek.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/QuickQuest.png" alt="QuickQuest Logo" style="max-width: 300px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
      <h2 style="color: #4FB8B3;">Payment Successful - Job Confirmation</h2>
    </div>
    <!-- Greeting -->
    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing QuickQuest for your service needs. We are pleased to inform you that your payment has been successfully processed, and your job is now confirmed.</p>
    <!-- Job ID and Details -->
    <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <h3 style="color: #4FB8B3;">Job Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Job ID:</strong> {{jobID}}</p>
      <p><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> ${{price}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date Ordered:</strong> {{orderedDate}}</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Worker Details -->
    <div style="background-color: #e0f7fa; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <h3 style="color: #4FB8B3;">Worker Assigned</h3>
      <p>We have carefully selected a qualified and experienced worker to handle your job:</p>
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{workerName}}</p>
      <p><strong>Contact:</strong> {{workerContact}}</p>
      <p>Your assigned worker will reach out to you shortly to discuss further details and arrange the service delivery.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Next Steps -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <h3 style="color: #4FB8B3;">What's Next?</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Your worker will contact you to finalize the service details and schedule.</li>
        <li>The worker will complete the job within the agreed-upon timeframe.</li>
        <li>Once the job is completed, please log in to your QuickQuest account to review and provide feedback.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <!-- Customer Support -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or require further assistance, our customer support team is here to help.</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@quickquest.com" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #4FB8B3; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Contact Customer Support</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;">
      <p>Thank you for using QuickQuest. We look forward to serving you and ensuring your satisfaction.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>